snippet.title: Gallic Wars: Battle Simulator - PC Gameplay (Steam)
snippet.description:
Time to conquer ROME! Become a commander of Gallic Warriors and destroy Roman Empire in this Rouge-like strategy game.

Developed by MadGamesmith
Published by WIG Publishing
Also released for Xbox One, Xbox Series X|S and Nintendo Switch
